Bus from Torshavn. 
If going by car it's beyond the road tunnel to the airport.

There are two firms running boat trips to see birds and caves. These are awe inspiring as the boat weaves around stacks, through arches and into caves; arctic and great skuas and gannets can be seen as well as puffins, common and black guillemots, razorbills, fulmars and arctic terns galore.
The Vestmanna Tourist Centre has a restaurant. The Centre is open from 9 am to 5 pm all days during summer (may through september)
